{"tid":2401310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登一上台，就放生抖音係美國發展廣告業務","createTime":"2021-02-09T15:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T16:37:15.000Z","uid":113951,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ba5ff52d144757b6ffb1d5ede3a678fe8698299f","tid":2401310,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:25:13.000Z","msg":"大家學好普通話未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n// Bloomberg報導，抖音宣佈將夥拍全球最大的廣告集團WPP，合作力攻美國市場，大推兩天前文章分析的那三種「短視頻」平台盈利模式。<br />\n<br />\n雖然之前Trump任內力禁抖音在美國流行(或者最少先由美國公司控制)，可惜最後因為遇到深層國家操控的各地法院從中作梗，以致商務部未能中止抖音營運。但今日拜登上台，抖音就立即重新上路了。 <br />\n<br />\n「打賞」一向是快手的重要收入，早年佔總收入近九成，上年頭三季中亦佔約六成，其餘為廣告收入(三成多)和主播賣貨抽佣(約5%)。<br />\n//<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/601e06303fa4830cf8e3a867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F601e06303fa4830cf8e3a867&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQqC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=aa7224dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/601e06303fa4830cf8e3a867</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6022a7457a916f575436ea0f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F6022a7457a916f575436ea0f&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQqC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=b613e945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6022a7457a916f575436ea0f</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-02-07/tiktok-plans-u-s-e-commerce-expansion-with-new-features-ft\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2021-02-07%2Ftiktok-plans-u-s-e-commerce-expansion-with-new-features-ft&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQqC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=f69f3e52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-02-07/tiktok-plans-u-s-e-commerce-expansion-with-new-features-ft</a>